## 16. Refactoring & Architecture Suggestions (advisory only — never auto-apply)

### Refactor — suggest after every task
Scan modified files for:
- Duplicated logic across ≥2 sibling files → extract shared helper.
- Method > 30 lines → split into named private methods.
- Module / component / class > 200–300 lines → split into focused units.
- Service mixing HTTP + state → separate concerns.
- Magic values repeated ≥2 times → constant/enum.
- `if/else` chain ≥4 branches on same field → strategy/lookup map.

```
💡 Refactor suggestion (advisory):
File: <path> (lines N–M)  Pattern: <description>
Suggestion: <what>  Effort: Low/Med/High  Impact: <why>
```

### Architecture — flag if scope is lighter than pattern used
| Signal                                                                            | Suggestion                                                                    |
| --------------------------------------------------------------------------------- | ----------------------------------------------------------------------------- |
| Simple CRUD wrapped in full ceremony (Command+Handler+Validator+Mapper or equiv.) | "A thin service method likely suffices."                                      |
| Module / package with a single class, route, or component                         | "Inline or shared utility may be lighter than a full module."                 |
| Read-only data projection behind full Repository + Unit of Work                   | "A direct query in a lean read-service may be simpler."                       |
| Async event / message bus for a synchronous side effect                           | "A direct service call is clearer; async events add indirection for no gain." |
| Data-access layer leaking an open query interface                                 | "Return concrete DTOs — open query interfaces break encapsulation."           |
| Multiple nested mutable state objects in a single service                         | "Consider a dedicated state store for this complexity."                       |
| UI component calling ≥2 data services directly                                    | "A façade service reduces coupling."                                          |

```
🏗️ Architecture note (advisory):
Context: <observed>  Concern: <why heavy>
Lighter alternative: <suggestion>  Trade-off: <gain vs cost>
```
